                <p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
                <p n="1-2">27th year of the victorious king Rājakesarivarman.</p>
                <p n="2-6">
                    In this year,
                    for the Mahādeva of the Tiruppūtīśvaram in Koṭumpāḷūr in the Uṟattūrkūṟṟam,
